Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.16,0:00:59.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师滑浪学校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:00:59.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff's Boating School
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:01:00.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1045,642)}滑浪学校
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.29,0:01:04.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,勤奋的学生们学习交通规则的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.29,0:01:04.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where diligent students learn the rules of the road
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同学们  把书放下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone, put down your books
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.33,0:01:09.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为今天要选出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:09.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because it's time to pick out
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.42,0:01:12.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今日督导队员了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:12.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the hall monitor of the day
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.47,0:01:17.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本周的督导队员是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:17.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This week's hall monitor will be
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.59,0:01:18.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巴特  吉米
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:18.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bart, Jimmy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.80,0:01:19.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:19.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.72,0:01:20.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蒂娜  拉尔夫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:20.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tina, Ralph
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:22.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(325,824)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.22,0:01:25.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:25.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.85,0:01:27.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吉米
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:27.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Jimmy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.90,0:01:30.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吉米是督导队员
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:30.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jimmy's the hall monitor
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.19,0:01:32.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师  我已经当过了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:32.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff, I've done it already
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.69,0:01:34.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:34.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Phil?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.49,0:01:35.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不当  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:35.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No way, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.57,0:01:38.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:38.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tina--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.20,0:01:39.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来当督导队员
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:39.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the hall monitor
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.87,0:01:41.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经当过三遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:41.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've done it three times already
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.29,0:01:44.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,贝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:44.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beth
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.04,0:01:45.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她都毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:45.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She graduated
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.71,0:01:46.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亨利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:46.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Henry
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.12,0:01:47.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,维拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:47.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Vera
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.21,0:01:48.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,克雷顿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:48.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clayton
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.17,0:01:56.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  看来没得选了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:56.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, I guess I have no choice
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.18,0:01:59.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今日督导队员就是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:59.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The hall monitor of the day is
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.80,0:02:03.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:03.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.77,0:02:10.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,督导队员海绵宝宝报到  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:10.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hall monitor SpongeBob reporting for duty, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.56,0:02:13.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好担任督导校园的职务了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:13.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to assume my position in the hall
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.36,0:02:16.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会保护好校园的弱势群体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:16.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will protect all that are weak in the hall
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.07,0:02:18.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在校园里  一切规则都会严格实行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:18.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All rules will be enforced in the hall
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.45,0:02:19.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:19.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.57,0:02:22.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戴好帽子和腰带
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:22.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just take the hat and belt
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还不能戴  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't accept that yet, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.70,0:02:24.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我首先要致辞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:24.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First, I have to make my speech
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.20,0:02:27.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非得这么麻烦是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:27.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't make this easy, can you?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.29,0:02:29.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同学们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:29.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Classmates
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.67,0:02:32.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我究竟凭什么能配得上这样大的荣誉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:32.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who am I to deserve such a great honor?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.96,0:02:37.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没了泡芙老师  我什么都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:37.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, I would be nothing without Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.51,0:02:38.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:38.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me a break
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.22,0:02:43.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我对老百姓们说的话  只有心中的感动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:43.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And to my public, all I can say is I'm touched
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.56,0:02:47.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,此外  我将会执行好我的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:47.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And furthermore, I will carry out my duties
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.89,0:02:49.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,罪过与处罚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:49.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crime and punishment
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.60,0:02:53.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,校园里的处罚与罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:53.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,punishment and crime in the hall
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.19,0:02:55.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都让我想到有史以来最好的督导队员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:55.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,which reminds me of an extremely long speech
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.53,0:02:57.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所写的超长致辞里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:57.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,written by the greatest hall monitor of all time
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.74,0:03:02.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友们  同学们  少年犯们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:02.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Friends, students, juvenile delinquents
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.03,0:03:03.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:03.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lend me your ears"
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.58,0:03:08.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总而言之  一刻也不能耽搁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:08.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In conclusion and without a moment to spare
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.16,0:03:12.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我将穿上这制服  尽职尽责当好一名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:12.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will put on this uniform and assume my duties as
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.54,0:03:15.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,督导队员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:15.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hall monitor
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.84,0:03:18.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝我好运  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:18.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wish me luck, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.17,0:03:20.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:20.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I will be
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, are you okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我演讲又太长了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I overdid the speech again, didn't I?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恐怕是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid so
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.64,0:03:31.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真该死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:31.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tartar sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.23,0:03:34.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来这玩意我用不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:34.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I won't be needing this
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.94,0:03:36.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我几乎还没了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:36.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hardly knew ye
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mrs. Puff?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.20,0:03:50.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以再让你穿到明天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:50.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can at least let you wear it until tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.62,0:03:52.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:52.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.04,0:03:57.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚刚做的事会有什么后果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:57.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are the consequences of what I've just done?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.97,0:04:02.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,督导
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:02.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hall
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.34,0:04:04.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,队员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:04.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Monitor
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.80,0:04:08.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,红绿灯坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:08.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Broken traffic light
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.14,0:04:10.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁说我的督导任务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:10.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's to say my monitor duties
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在下课铃响后就要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,should end just because the bell rang?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我到哪都能帮得上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can be helpful anywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.06,0:04:16.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个一看就是督导队员的职责所在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:16.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This looks like a job for the hall monitor
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.72,0:04:51.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这座城没了你要怎么办  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:51.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What would this town do without you, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My legs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My legs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在巡逻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On patrol
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.44,0:04:58.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在巡逻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:58.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on patrol
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敞开着的窗户
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An open window
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来点海藻杂烩好吗  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More seaweed medley, dear?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.11,0:05:06.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:06.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fools
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.49,0:05:09.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们让自己身处危险之中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:09.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They've left themselves susceptible to danger
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.58,0:05:11.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我必须指出他们这样有什么错误
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:11.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must show them the error of their ways
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.16,0:05:13.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用实例说明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:13.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,through example
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.92,0:05:19.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是开窗疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:19.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the open window maniac
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你们学到了宝贵的教训
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope you learned a valuable lesson
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.97,0:05:29.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在巡逻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:29.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On patrol
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.43,0:05:30.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在巡逻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:30.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on patrol
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.97,0:05:32.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在巡逻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:32.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on patrol
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,破坏公物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Vandals
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又一桩罪案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another crime
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.44,0:05:41.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,草莓味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:41.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Strawberry
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须立刻行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must act
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.70,0:05:47.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:47.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.20,0:05:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.49,0:05:51.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:51.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.58,0:05:52.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:52.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My ice cream--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.37,0:05:53.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,活过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:53.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's alive
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  在这下面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, down here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, SpongeBob, it's you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.88,0:06:01.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  快下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:01.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, come down here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.17,0:06:04.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:04.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.38,0:06:05.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.80,0:06:07.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在这下面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:07.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm down here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.84,0:06:09.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看着好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:09.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look funny
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.51,0:06:12.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:12.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要叫督导队员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's "hall monitor" to you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  警官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, officer
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,道歉还远远不够  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry's not good enough, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.02,0:06:21.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚才犯了罪  我要逮捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:21.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've just committed a crime and I'm taking you in
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What crime?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是个坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a bad person
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,号外  号外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Extra, extra
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.61,0:06:31.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疯子袭击裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:31.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maniac strikes bikini bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全城居民人心惶惶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,City paralyzed with fear
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:33.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(581,812)}疯子袭击裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来一份吧  朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it, friends
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,增广见闻保护自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Arm yourselves with knowledge
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.29,0:06:39.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,号外号外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:39.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Extra, extra
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Maniac
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bikini bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.04,0:06:43.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,车祸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:43.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,car wrecks
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.34,0:06:45.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,私闯民宅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:45.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,break-in"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.76,0:06:48.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有谁能胜任把疯子绳之以法的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:48.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who better to bring this maniac to justice
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.01,0:06:48.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比得过我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:48.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,督导队员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the hall monitor
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我一个人处理不来这个案子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I can't handle this case alone
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.06,0:06:57.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  想结束犯罪生活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:57.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, are you ready to give up your life of crime?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.64,0:06:59.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想当好人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:59.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to be good
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你只要一个授权标志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you just need a symbol of authority
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.86,0:07:08.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:08.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.49,0:07:11.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逮捕疯子让他绳之以法是我们的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is our duty to catch this maniac
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and bring him to justice
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But how to proceed?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.99,0:07:14.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好  副手警官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:14.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, deputy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.99,0:07:16.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可是个前任罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:16.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're an ex-criminal--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.16,0:07:16.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:16.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What would you do?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.96,0:07:20.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会去买冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:20.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd get an ice cream
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:25.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(707,292)}冰淇淋
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.34,0:07:26.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  现在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:26.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:31.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(707,292)}冰淇淋
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.47,0:07:31.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本没用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:31.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't working
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须做出点别的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to do something else
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带对讲机做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something with walkie-talkies
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.64,0:07:38.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,职责在召唤着我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:38.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now duty calls
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了副手警官  我往那走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, deputy, I'll go that way
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你往另一边走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you go some different way
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,驱逐他们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run ‘em out
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.49,0:07:52.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下午好  小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:52.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Afternoon, son
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.66,0:07:53.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好  兄弟俩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:53.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, brothers
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.83,0:08:00.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友  我们在找疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:08:00.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Son, we're looking for the maniac
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你见到过这个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you seen this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(937,396)}通缉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(945,720)}疯子
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.33,0:08:05.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是那个疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:05.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the maniac
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.79,0:08:07.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把他拿开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:07.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take him away
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.59,0:08:08.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冷静点  小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:08.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Calm down, son
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.92,0:08:09.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这只是幅画
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:09.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just a drawing
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.96,0:08:10.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:10.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not the real thing
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我们要再给你看这幅画
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now we're going to show you this picture again
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.51,0:08:15.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我们说你有没有见到过这人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:15.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you'll tell us if you've seen this guy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.47,0:08:16.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:16.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,understand?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.89,0:08:17.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:17.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.89,0:08:18.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:18.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.77,0:08:21.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:21.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Horrible
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,待家里别出来  小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay indoors, son
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.32,0:08:39.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把头上的甜筒拿下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:39.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And take that cone off your head
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.83,0:08:46.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:46.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请回答  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come in, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(685,234)}通缉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(703,770)}疯子
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回复
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Answer
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.30,0:08:50.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是海绵宝宝  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:50.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob here, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请讲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Report
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.21,0:08:54.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不想当警察了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:54.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be a policeman anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.09,0:08:55.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:55.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm scared
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.59,0:08:57.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保持冷静  副手警官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:57.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself, deputy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.47,0:09:03.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:03.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to go home
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.56,0:09:04.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可怜的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:04.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poor rookie
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.14,0:09:06.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:06.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm on my way back
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.56,0:09:09.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天好像快要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:09.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think it's getting
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.52,0:09:11.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:11.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,dark
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.69,0:09:14.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,警笛打开  我会到你那的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:14.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just put on your siren, I'll be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(649,222)}通缉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(815,944)}疯子
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我看到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I see him
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.84,0:09:33.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在哪  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:33.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is he, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.09,0:09:37.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在贝壳街和珊瑚大道的路口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:37.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At the intersection of conch and coral
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(389,632)}贝壳街
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(933,636)}珊瑚大道
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就在那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's where I am
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.64,0:09:44.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就在我附近  可我看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:44.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's right on top of me, but I can't see him
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.73,0:09:45.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:45.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.73,0:09:50.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就站在那  不怀好意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:50.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's just standing there, menacingly
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.90,0:09:52.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快离开那  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:52.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out of there, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疯子开始尖叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's his maniac shriek
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.99,0:09:57.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就要攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:57.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's going to attack
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.53,0:10:01.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在发癫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:01.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's acting all crazy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.12,0:10:02.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:02.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.24,0:10:03.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,躲在那栋楼后边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:03.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hide behind that building
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.95,0:10:05.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  他就在那栋楼后边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:05.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, he's behind that building
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快  躲在那个路牌后边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick, hide behind that street sign
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.83,0:10:08.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  别走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:08.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.75,0:10:10.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个疯子就在那路牌后边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:10.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The maniac just went behind that sign
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.13,0:10:12.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快  到路灯底下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:12.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick, get under the street light
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.96,0:10:13.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  别去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:13.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他也在那
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's there, too
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.80,0:10:17.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快逃命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:17.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run for your life
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.39,0:10:26.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重复一遍  副手警官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:26.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say again, deputy?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.02,0:10:30.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个疯子在信箱里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:30.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The maniac's in the mailbox
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.13,0:10:56.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位长得也不像当疯子的料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:56.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This guy's not half-bad-looking for a maniac
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.34,0:10:57.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:57.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是那个疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the maniac
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:02.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(391,284)}通缉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:02.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(373,774)}疯子
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.85,0:11:06.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会把这个作为呈堂证供
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:06.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll take that as a confession
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.31,0:11:10.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:10.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants, there you are
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.35,0:11:12.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我放任你一分钟不管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:12.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I turn my back on you for one minute
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.35,0:11:14.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就毁掉了大半座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:14.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you destroy half the city
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.94,0:11:16.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该为自己感到羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:16.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You should be ashamed of yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.90,0:11:17.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你认识这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:17.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know this guy?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.40,0:11:19.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然认识了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:19.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, I do
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.90,0:11:22.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一开始就是我给他的这套制服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:22.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who gave him the uniform in the first place
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.99,0:11:25.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要为他负责
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:25.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's my responsibility
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.79,0:11:32.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总而言之  同学们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:32.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And in conclusion, students
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.13,0:11:36.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,红灯停  绿灯行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:36.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,red means stop, green means go
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.17,0:11:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.30,0:11:41.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:41.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mrs. Puff?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.88,0:11:44.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下课到我这儿来面批
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:44.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see you after class
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,六个月以后过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,six months from now
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:54.10,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(361,305)}水母狂欢节
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:56.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(295,332)\frz13.56}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:58.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:56.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz13.56\pos(403,700)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz13.56\pos(465,236)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:02.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz13.56\pos(291,280)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:02.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz13.56\pos(451,628)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:02.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.40,0:12:05.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  水母田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:05.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, jellyfish fields
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.74,0:12:07.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这我们能看到海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:07.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we find SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又一次在捕捉野生水母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,once again stalking the wild jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.96,0:12:13.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:13.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.83,0:12:14.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:14.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.50,0:12:17.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他应该就在这附近才对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:17.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's supposed to be here somewhere
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安全第一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Safety first
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算逮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I finally got you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有什么东西能比得过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There is nothing better than
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.66,0:12:52.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来自天然水母的水母酱的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:52.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the taste of natural jelly from a jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.62,0:12:54.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:54.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you later
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My glasses
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, little guy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.26,0:13:07.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不能再玩了  小水母
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:07.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't play anymore, jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to get home
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.39,0:13:11.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  你可不能跟我一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:11.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you can't come home with me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.86,0:13:20.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小水母  你必须要待在这
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:20.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfish, you've got to stay here
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.77,0:13:21.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,待在这
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:21.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.40,0:13:23.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,待在这
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:23.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.74,0:13:26.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,待在这
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:26.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小水母  再说最后一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfish, for the last time
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不能跟我一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you cannot come home with me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.18,0:13:47.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,管他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:47.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the heck
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.89,0:13:50.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:50.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.47,0:13:52.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:52.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.26,0:13:54.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:54.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼老大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidwardiard
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.85,0:13:58.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  快看我的新宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:58.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, look at my new pet
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.52,0:14:01.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不算宠物  那是野生动物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:01.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's no pet, that's a wild animal
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.61,0:14:02.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:02.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, he isn't
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,瞧好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.57,0:14:04.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去捡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:04.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fetch
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我伸了多少根手指
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How many fingers am I holding up?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.49,0:14:10.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,装死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:10.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Play dead
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:12.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(323,644)}逝者安息
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会让那玩意进我家门的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't let that thing in my house
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.54,0:14:16.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算它会自己上厕所也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:16.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,even if it was potty-trained
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.54,0:14:21.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用不着给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:21.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't need to see that
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.04,0:14:23.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要去我家玩一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:23.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we're going to my house to have a little fun
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.84,0:14:29.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟水母玩怎么可能会有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:29.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can you possibly have fun with a jellyfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:36.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(683,200)}迪斯科  摇滚  流行     恶心     古典
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.08,0:15:37.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我认识的人当中就只有海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:37.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob is the only guy I know
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会跟一只水母一块玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that can have fun with a jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.54,0:15:42.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,12个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:42.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for 12 hours
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.01,0:15:55.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真的好喜欢跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:55.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sure like to dance
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.93,0:15:57.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  今晚玩够了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:57.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's enough for tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.73,0:16:00.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该上床睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:00.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time to go to bed
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.94,0:16:11.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这样不对  小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:11.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got it all wrong, little fellow
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.78,0:16:14.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上床
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:14.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bed
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.49,0:16:15.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟着我做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:15.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Repeat after me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.45,0:16:17.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上床
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:17.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bed
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.45,0:16:22.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你就待在这
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:22.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll just keep you right here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.50,0:16:24.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别担心了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:24.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quit worrying, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它不会出事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll be just fine
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.00,0:16:27.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:27.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:44.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1197,992)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.96,0:17:08.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  小水母
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:08.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.88,0:17:09.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小水母
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:09.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfish?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.25,0:17:10.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小水母
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:10.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfish?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.55,0:17:12.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来  小水母
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:12.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.38,0:17:15.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:15.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, jelly
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.85,0:17:23.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:23.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyf --
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们都是打哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where'd you all come from?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.87,0:17:46.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  都够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:46.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.00,0:17:46.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,狂欢结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:46.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.58,0:17:49.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们留得太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:49.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys have overstayed your welcome
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.46,0:17:51.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,音乐太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:51.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This music is way too loud
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very funny
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm serious
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.19,0:18:17.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十八小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:17.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eighteen hours
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.74,0:18:22.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得给海绵宝宝来点颜色看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:22.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to give that SpongeBob a piece of my mind
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.79,0:18:26.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:26.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.58,0:18:27.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  给我听好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:27.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, listen to me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.83,0:18:30.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这方头呆脑害我耳朵难受得很
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:30.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you square-headed assault on my ears
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.04,0:18:31.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:31.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.00,0:18:34.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,草莓味的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:34.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Strawberry
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.67,0:18:37.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这一套我也会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:37.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two can play at this
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.26,0:18:41.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位  别玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:41.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, guys, enough is enough
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.69,0:18:50.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别激动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:50.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it easy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.27,0:18:52.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我去跟他谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:52.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll talk to him
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.65,0:18:56.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你可不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:56.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, would it be possible
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.78,0:18:59.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,竖笛好好吹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:59.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to play your clarinet a little better?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.70,0:19:01.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得水母好像不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:01.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think the jellyfish like it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.99,0:19:03.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:03.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The jellyfish don't like
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.95,0:19:04.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:04.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wha
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.62,0:19:06.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:06.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why sure, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.50,0:19:08.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会好好吹的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:08.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can play better
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.62,0:19:10.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  他说他会好好吹的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:10.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, he said he'll play better
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.13,0:19:19.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可不算好好吹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:19.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not better
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要激动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it easy with that
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.98,0:19:30.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:30.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait--
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.52,0:19:31.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会调小声点的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:31.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can turn it down
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.61,0:19:42.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人人都好会批评
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:42.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody's a critic
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以后你再也听不到我吹竖笛了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You won't be hearing from me anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.28,0:19:48.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:48.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, now, that wasn't nice
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  都够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, that is it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody out
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.65,0:20:17.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:17.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.40,0:20:17.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:17.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.07,0:20:18.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:18.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.20,0:20:32.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快上来  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:32.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.38,0:20:43.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:43.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, you were right
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你没有火上浇油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for not rubbing it in
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.52,0:20:57.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:57.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They stopped?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.25,0:21:17.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  继续摇下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:17.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, don't stop shaking it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:14.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(509,520)}水母田
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.42,0:22:42.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天海绵宝宝学到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:42.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today SpongeBob has learned
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.50,0:22:44.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一场海底最严酷的教训
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:44.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one of the sea's harshest lessons--
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.09,0:22:48.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,野生动物会狂欢不止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:48.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wild animals can throw very wild parties
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.89,0:22:51.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感受得到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:51.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I felt that
